title: The Adventure Zone: Live In Atlanta!
description: We're running behind on the next episode of Amnesty, so in it's stead, here's our most recent live show from Atlanta, GA! Follow Tres Horny Boys and their inscrutable companion on a journey across the planes as they learn the horrible history of one of their iconic armaments.
author: shows@themcelroy.family (The McElroys)
